comments.body: Although now more than 10 populations in L.A. County, this population was the first established population in Ventura County. We published this new county record back in 2015: Larson et al., Herpetological Review 46, page 59.

results.place_guess: 110-120 W Easy St, Simi Valley, CA 93065, USA
